<section id="faq" class="palette flexy">
    <hgroup class="flexy">
        <h2 id="frequently-asked-questions-faq" title="Frequently asked questions FAQ">Frequently asked questions FAQ</h2>
        <p>We have answers (well, most of the times&excl;)</p>
        <p>Below you&apos;ll find answers to the most common questions you may have on Rapid&period; If you still can&apos;t find the answer you&apos;re looking for&comma; just <a href="/contact/" title="Contact us">contact us</a>&excl;</p>
